
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Starter Guide";
}


<style>
    body {
        font-family: sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    main {
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .additional-resources {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .card-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 20px;
        margin: 0 5%;
    }

    .card {
        flex: 0 0 calc(33.33% - 20px);
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 20px;
        transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

       

        .card a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #193631;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            width: 45%;
            text-align: center;
            align-self: center;
        }  

    .resource-list {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding: 0;
    }
 
    .card a:hover {
        background-color: #193631;
    } 

    h1{
        padding: 5%;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .header{
        background-color: #193631;
        margin-bottom: 2%;
    }
</style>



<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Garden Starter Guide</title>

</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Garden Starter Guide</h1>
    </div>
    <main>
        <section class="card-container">

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Choosing a Location</h3>
                <p>The first step in starting a garden is choosing the right location. Your garden should be in a sunny spot with well-drained soil. It should also be close to a water source.</p>
                <a href="#">See More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Planning Your Garden</h3>
                <p>Once you've chosen a location, it's time to start planning your garden. Decide what crops you want to grow and how much space you need for each one. You can use a garden planner to help you lay out your garden.</p>
                <a href="#">See More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Planting your Crops</h3>
                <p>When you're ready to plant your crops, be sure to follow the instructions on the seed packet. Plant your seeds at the proper depth and spacing. Water your seeds regularly and keep the soil moist.</p>
                <a href="#">See More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Maintaining Your Garden</h3>
                <p>When you're ready to plant your crops, be sure to follow the instructions on the seed packet. Plant your seeds at the proper depth and spacing. Water your seeds regularly and keep the soil moist.</p>
                <a href="ManageGarden">See Garden</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Harvesting your Crops</h3>
                <p>When your crops are ripe, it's time to harvest them. Be sure to harvest your crops at the right time to ensure the best flavor and quality.</p>
                <a href="#">See More</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="additional-resources">
            <h2>Additional Resources</h2>
            <p>Here are some additional resources that you may find helpful:</p>
            <ul class="resourceList">
                <li><a href="https://www.almanac.com/gardening">The Old Farmer's Almanac</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://garden.org/">The National Gardening Association</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.ahs.org/">The American Horticultural Society</a></li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>Copyright 2023 Sustainable Farming Resources</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
